Puck=E2=80=99s best new reporting.

=C2=A0

First up today, Dylan Byers digs into all the reasons Disney decided to set=
tle the Trump defamation case=E2=80=94from an unfavorable Florida judge to =
discovery fears surrounding George Stephanopoulos=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Csloppy=
